instructions:
Tag	Meaning	Embed color
[Trusted]	Verified safe source	🟢 Green
[Mod]	Modified app	🟠 Orange
[Tweaked]	Tweaked/patched app	🟣 Purple
[Cracked]	Cracked/unlocked app	🔴 Red
[Official]	Official release	🔵 Blue


Download Fields
Field	Meaning
APPSTORE:	Link to App Store page. Put none to skip.
GITHUBDIRECTDOWNLOAD:	Official IPA hosted on GitHub. Put none to skip.
UNOFFICIALDOWNLOAD:	Unverified 3rd party link — shows ⚠️ Untrusted
UNOFFICIALDOWNLOADTRUSTED:	Community-verified link — shows ✅ Trusted Unofficial
ICON:	App icon thumbnail (.png .jpg .jpeg .webp .webm .gif)
